pageContext.claim: “If Shifty Adam Schiff, who is a corrupt politician who fraudulently made up what I said on the 'call,' is allowed to release transcripts of the Never Trumpers & others that are & were interviewed, he will change the words that were said to suit the Dems purposes.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence the transcripts of depositions were changed. Prior to public release, the witnesses were able to review them to insure they were accurately quoted.
